{"tid":630783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"戒丁勸世文","createTime":"2018-04-16T01:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T03:55:47.000Z","uid":104092,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ee3607ee71fdb6990a93fbc7e283e9296e4767a0","tid":630783,"uid":104092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T01:55:24.000Z","msg":"小弟今年24歲 小學開始打飛機<br />\n打左十幾年 舊陣時打得好癲<br />\n試過一星期打足六日 又試過連續兩日打六次<br />\n當時血氣方剛 長打長有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到大學開始住宿舍 收斂左啲<br />\n但係一個星期都會打三四次<br />\n住hall無王管 經常通宵打機飲酒<br />\nyr2就仆街啦 啲精唔再係射出黎 係流出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時都知道大撚鑊 已經盡量打少啲<br />\n但係戒丁話咁易咩 努力控制一星期打一兩次<br />\n點知條丁每況愈下<br />\n屌你老母 yr3連晨勃都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前睇J圖已經會硬 宜家要睇a片先硬到<br />\n我條J已經透支左 唔知要養幾耐先回復到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好懷念以前晚晚扯住黎瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以係到勸下大家 打少啲丁<br />\n早睡早起 均衡飲食 養成良好生活習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6761d0de3748b244a7860d3749e4dd38ceb52d","tid":630783,"uid":72396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T01:58:50.000Z","msg":"想知有無禿頭"},{"pid":"b87f668eb22dd51f856c9bd34fc142789116946f","tid":630783,"uid":104092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f6761d0de3748b244a7860d3749e4dd38ceb52d","tid":630783,"uid":72396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T01:58:50.000Z","msg":"想知有無禿頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T02:32:16.000Z","msg":"頭髮濃密 飛髮佬話我髮質好好"},{"pid":"b796dbf823ec16d29b98e047df5301d9e1496776","tid":630783,"uid":104092,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T02:34:33.000Z","msg":"比負皮嗰啲係唔係日日沉醉打丁 唔肯面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade25280e6701810bc9c5f35a1246c72d94cfe2d","tid":630783,"uid":2966,